column4: Delphi  Mobileye to use Intel chip for self-driving car system
column5: Nov 29 Auto parts maker Delphi Automotive Plc  and Israeli technology firm Mobileye NV will put an Intel Corp chip at the heart of their joint effort to produce self-driving vehicles by 2019  the companies said on Tuesday.
